## 4. 📋 Booking Management

| Detail | Info |
|---|---|
| **Route** | `/booking` |
| **Controller** | [BookingController.php](file:///d:/ServiceHub/app/Http/Controllers/Backend/BookingController.php) |
| **Pricing Logic** | [PricingEngine.php](file:///d:/ServiceHub/app/Services/PricingEngine.php) |

### 🎯 Purpose (ये Module क्यों बना है):
> **ये पूरे system का सबसे important module है — इसी से business चलता है।** हर shifting order एक "Booking" है। Admin यहाँ से manually booking create कर सकता है (जब customer phone पर call करके booking करवाता है), existing bookings edit कर सकता है, status change कर सकता है। **PricingEngine** automatically items, distance, add-ons, surcharges के basis पर price calculate करता है ताकि manual calculation की ग़लतियाँ न हों। Booking का पूरा lifecycle (pending → confirmed → in_progress → completed/cancelled) यहीं से manage होता है।

### क्या काम करता है:

| Action | Description |
|---|---|
| **List** | सभी bookings DataTable में — booking number, customer, mobile, date/time, amount, status |
| **Create (➕)** | New booking — customer search (AJAX), pickup/drop location, items select, add-ons, floor, date/time |
| **View (👁)** | Full detail — customer info, locations, items, add-ons, pricing breakdown, vehicle, category |
| **Edit (✏️)** | Update booking — items/addons बदलने पर **price auto re-calculate** |
| **Cancel (❌)** | Booking cancel (status → cancelled) |
| **Complete (✅)** | Booking complete mark (status → completed) |

### Booking Statuses:
| Status | Badge | Meaning |
|---|---|---|
| `pending` | 🟡 | Booking बनी है, confirm नहीं हुई |
| `confirmed` | 🔵 | Booking confirm हो गई |
| `in_progress` | 🔵 | Shifting जारी है |
| `completed` | 🟢 | Shifting पूरी हो गई |
| `cancelled` | 🔴 | Booking cancel हो गई |

### Auto Pricing (PricingEngine) कैसे काम करता है:
```
Step 1 → Items का Volume Score calculate (item score × quantity)
Step 2 → Score > 310 → "Survey Required" (बहुत बड़ा shifting, manual quote ज़रूरी)
Step 3 → Volume Score से auto Category & Vehicle select
Step 4 → Distance charges — Haversine formula से km, first 5 km free, बाकी ₹20/km
Step 5 → Add-On charges जोड़ो
Step 6 → Floor charges (₹150/floor — बिना lift के)
Step 7 → Weekend surcharge (+10%) & Month-end surcharge (+15%)
Step 8 → Grand Total = Base + Distance + Addons + Floor + Weekend + Month-end
```

### Payment Breakdown:
| Item | Calculation |
|---|---|
| Advance Amount | Total × 20% |
| Remaining Amount | Total − Advance |
| Vendor Commission | Total × 15% |
| Vendor Settlement | Total − Commission |

