## 🔗 Mobile App API Endpoints

Admin panel के साथ एक **Customer Mobile App API** भी है:

### 🎯 Purpose: Customer **mobile app से** register, login, booking request भेजना, bookings देखना — ये सब API से होता है।

| Endpoint | Method | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| `/api/check-mobile` | POST | Mobile number registered है या नहीं check करो |
| `/api/register` | POST | New customer registration |
| `/api/verify-otp` | POST | OTP verify करो (login complete) |
| `/api/resend-otp` | POST | OTP दोबारा भेजो |
| `/api/logout` | POST | App logout |
| `/api/user` | GET | Current logged-in user details |
