## 📝 Models & Relationships

| Model | Purpose | Key Relationships |
|---|---|---|
| **User** | Customers + Admin/Staff दोनों | hasMany Bookings, has Roles (Spatie) |
| **Booking** | Core shifting order | belongsTo Customer, Category, Vehicle; belongsToMany Items, AddOns; hasOne Feedback |
| **BookingRequest** | App से आई request | belongsTo Customer → Approve = Booking बने |
| **Category** | Shifting category (1BHK, 2BHK) | belongsTo Vehicle, defines base_fare + score range |
| **Vehicle** | Transport vehicle | hasMany Categories |
| **Item** | Shifting item (Bed, Sofa) | belongsToMany Bookings, has volume_score |
| **AddOn** | Extra service (Packing, AC) | belongsToMany Bookings, has fixed price |
| **Feedback** | Customer review | belongsTo Booking + Customer |
| **Setting** | System config | Key-Value store (logo, favicon, footer) |
| **PricingSetting** | Pricing config | Key-Value (per_km_rate, floor_charge, surcharge %) |
| **OrderTracking** | Booking status history | belongsTo Booking |

